OL,7,FA mum called her five-year-old son in
OL,8,Ffrom playing in the street for his tea
OL,9,Fbut was met with a "piercing scream"
OL,10,Fas he was "dragged around like a toy"
OL,11,Fby an escaped dog.
OL,13,FAmy Briers' Shar Pei and Staffordshire
OL,14,Fbull terrier cross bit two children
OL,15,Fbefore her pet went on to attack
OL,16,Fanother three youngsters during two
OL,17,Ffurther incidents in, heard.
OL,19,FTwo boys needed surgery as a result of
OL,20,Ftheir horrific injuries.
