OL,3,CMum met with a 'piercing scream' as
OL,4,Cfive-year-old was 'dragged around' by
OL,5,Ca dog
OL,7,FThe 33-year-old's dog Callie had
OL,8,F"previously bitten two children",
OL,9,Fleading to her entering a "voluntary
OL,10,Fagreement" with to ensure that the dog
OL,11,Fwas muzzled and on a lead in public
OL,12,Fand constantly supervised around
OL,13,Fchildren and strangers.
OL,15,FBut, unbeknownst to her, her 11-year-
OL,16,Fold autistic son took the family pet
OL,17,Fout for a walk at around 6.30pm on
OL,18,FJuly 11 last year.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/15
