OL,3,CMum met with a 'piercing scream' as
OL,4,Cfive-year-old was 'dragged around' by
OL,5,Ca dog
OL,7,FCallum Ross, prosecuting, described
OL,8,Fhow the boy approached a group of
OL,9,Fother youngsters who were playing in
OL,10,Fthe street and "asked if they wanted
OL,11,Fto stroke the dog" and said it "had
OL,12,Fonly bitten one person".
OL,14,FOne of the children, an 11-year-old
OL,15,Fgirl, "stood back" due to her fear of
OL,16,Fdogs, but Callie "ran up to her and
OL,17,Fbit her right forearm".
