OL,3,CMum met with a 'piercing scream' as
OL,4,Cfive-year-old was 'dragged around' by
OL,5,Ca dog
OL,7,FShe was "scared and crying" as a
OL,8,Fresult of the incident. Her father
OL,9,Fcleaned and dressed her wounds after
OL,10,Fshe returned home, and she did not
OL,11,Frequire further medical treatment.
OL,13,FThen, on the evening of September 21,
OL,14,Fanother two boys, aged five and six,
OL,15,Fwere playing out but as the mum of the
OL,16,Fyounger boy called him inside for his
OL,17,Ftea at around 7pm, she "heard a
OL,18,Fpiercing scream".
