OL,4,Cfive-year-old was 'dragged around' by
OL,5,Ca dog
OL,7,FShe then found her son with bites and
OL,8,Fpuncture wounds deep into his arm. He
OL,9,Flater told her that Callie had run
OL,10,Ffrom Briers' address on Hempstead Road
OL,11,Fin St Helens and bitten him before
OL,12,F"dragging him around".
OL,14,FThe boy required surgery to repair
OL,15,Finjuries to his abdomen and left
OL,16,Fforearm. He may require further
OL,17,Fcosmetic surgery in the future.
