OL,3,CMum met with a 'piercing scream' as
OL,4,Cfive-year-old was 'dragged around' by
OL,5,Ca dog
OL,7,FThe second child's mum meanwhile
OL,8,Frecalled hearing "hysterical screams"
OL,9,Fand running outside to find her son in
OL,10,Ftears and with "blood dripping down
OL,11,Fhis arm" and his friend being "dragged
OL,12,Faround like a toy". Briers, who had
OL,13,Fbeen at her neighbour's house at the
OL,14,Ftime of the incident, attempted to
OL,15,Fintervene by kicking her dog.
OL,17,FThe six-year-old suffered serious
OL,18,Finjuries to his right arm and also
OL,19,Frequired an operation. He was said to
OL,20,Fstill have "had a chunk missing from
OL,21,Fhis arm" months afterwards.
