OL,4,Cfive-year-old was 'dragged around' by
OL,5,Ca dog
OL,7,FBriers told detectives under interview
OL,8,Fthat she did not know anything about
OL,9,Fthe earlier incident and that she did
OL,10,Fnot allow her son to take the dog out
OL,11,Fon his own.
OL,13,FIn relation to the second attack, she
OL,14,Fsaid her son "must have forgotten to
OL,15,Fshut the door behind him" and allowed
OL,16,FCallie to escape.
