OL,4,Cfive-year-old was 'dragged around' by
OL,5,Ca dog
OL,7,FThe mum-of-four also stated that she
OL,8,Fhad made previous unsuccessful
OL,9,Fattempts to rehome her pet, who has
OL,10,Fsince been destroyed with her
OL,11,Fagreement, by posting on Facebook and
OL,12,Fcontacting the Dog's Trust. Briers has
OL,13,Fno previous convictions.
OL,15,FJamie Baxter, defending, told the
OL,16,Fcourt: "This is a devastating case for
OL,17,Fall involved - the victims of the
OL,18,Fattacks, their families and also this
OL,19,Fdefendant and her family. There is no
OL,20,Fevidence of the dog having attacked
OL,21,Ftwo previous children, only one.
