OL,5,Ca dog
OL,7,F"After the incident, this defendant
OL,8,Fmade genuine efforts to try and rehome
OL,9,FCallie. As a result of her efforts
OL,10,Fproving to be fruitless, the two
OL,11,Ffurther incidents took place.
OL,13,F"She is a good person. She is a good
OL,14,Fmother, doing her best in challenging
OL,15,Fcircumstances.
OL,17,F"She has three children aged five, 11
OL,18,Fand 16. She is a single mother with a
OL,19,Flimited support network.
