OL,7,FMr Baxter added that his client's
OL,8,Fincarceration would have a profound
OL,9,Fimpact on her children, who would
OL,10,Flikely have to be placed into foster
OL,11,Fcare if she was locked up.
OL,13,FHe said: "The welfare of her children
OL,14,Fand the protection of the public can
OL,15,Fbe achieved by a suspended sentence."
