OL,7,FBriers, who also has a fourth child
OL,8,Faged 18, admitted three counts of
OL,9,Fowning a dangerously out of control
OL,10,Fdog causing injury. She was handed a
OL,11,Ftwo-year imprisonment suspended for
OL,12,Ftwo years, 100 hours of unpaid work
OL,13,Fand a rehabilitation activity
OL,14,Frequirement of up to 10 days, as well
OL,15,Fas being banned from keeping dogs for
OL,16,Flife.
