OL,7,FSentencing, Judge Ian Harris said:
OL,8,F"You displayed a woeful and criminal
OL,9,Flack of responsibility. It was your
OL,10,Fresponsibility to ensure that the dog
OL,11,Fwas safely kept.
OL,13,F"The injuries caused to the young
OL,14,Fchildren were a direct consequence of
OL,15,Fyour reckless behaviour. You bear sole
OL,16,Fresponsibility.
