OL,10,Fand I accept these sentiments as
OL,11,Fgenuine.
OL,13,F"You are concerned that, if you go
OL,14,Finto prison, your children will likely
OL,15,Fend up in the care of the local
OL,16,Fauthority. In my judgement, the the
OL,17,Feffects of your imprisonment would be
OL,18,Fcatastrophic."
